801,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"成龍這番話引起網友猜測是誰不敬業，紛紛從他的新片《鐵道飛虎》、《功夫瑜伽》推敲，王凱、「龍子」房祖名、黃子韜、王大陸、張藝興等人都成為目標。不過成龍不願意曝光名字，只希望那個人心裡有數，以後改進。而他在前一段訪問曾滿口誇黃子韜，黃子韜粉絲彷彿得到免死金牌似的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f574520af4e70789f4d2b937b33215a4081feae1","tid":56801,"uid":29851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"就咁睇標題同第一段以為講緊佢個過氣新抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，原來係另有其人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a2ed8cc19b6787590a708a6e38025b5f5f63a7","tid":56801,"uid":17235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:09:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪on9啦 <br />\n唐詩300首大部分係粵語音 <br />\n幾時 唔係文言文 係粵語 亦係古詩用 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唐詩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n越引越多自以為識好多嘅柒頭衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蝗語?文言?粵語?唐詩?古詩?宋詞? 搞番清楚先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個post呢到最好睇"},{"pid":"ac1f1c3834da90e20d4baf1348d841049297cfab","tid":56801,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成龍都要酸人地！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38216363cc4aae2d04f