ote><br />\n成龍份人係仆街 但係佢d戲冇得講 全世界黎講佢係最有資格屌人拍戲既態度"},{"pid":"583baec787e95d5c101a2044a21a69218d3f0908","tid":56801,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成龍這番話引起網友猜測是誰不敬業，紛紛從他的新片《鐵道飛虎》、《功夫瑜伽》推敲，王凱、「龍子」房祖名、黃子韜、王大陸、張藝興等人都成為目標。不過成龍不願意曝光名字，只希望那個人心裡有數，以後改進。而他在前一段訪問曾滿口誇黃子韜，黃子韜粉絲彷彿得到免死金牌似的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係呢幾條友既<br />\n真係得王凱同王大陸兩個有可能<br />\n話晒張興藝都係KPOP涯過, 應該唔會咁樣<br />\n咁王凱同王大陸, 佢地係咩人我唔清楚, 但佢地最大分別係, 一個大陸人, 一個台灣人<br />\n我打死都唔信係大陸果個比人屌<br />\n咁最後剩返一個可能性就係王大陸"},{"pid":"2c667e5e321b4ad3b9e8d8f60c84ba62b6b6be2f","tid":56801,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪on9啦 <br />\n唐詩300首大部分係粵語音 <br />\n幾時 唔係文言文 係粵語 亦係古詩用 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唐詩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n越引越多自以為識好多嘅柒頭衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蝗語?文言?粵語?唐詩?古詩?宋詞? 搞番清楚先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個post呢到最好睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d46d7d58b801ce99e0ca65494d2383915c8c7a","tid":56801,"uid":40273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母陳港生你最敬業！！！拍拍下戲捉撚咗個女主角入叢林屌閪最敬業！！！！！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有故事？磨牙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係，之前有人爆過，女主角而家仲好紅（喺蝗國 ）"},{"pid":"af65e80d78f67d0c4cae4a4fae831c91140389aa","tid":56801,"uid":3138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母陳港生你最敬業！！！拍拍下戲捉撚咗個女主角入叢林屌閪最敬業！！！！！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有故事？磨牙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係，之前有人爆過，女主角而家仲好紅（喺蝗國 ）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未聽過"},{"pid":"56ba27d641fe610e52ca9c2a1506cdaaa95a1522","tid":56801,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母陳港生你最敬業！！！拍拍下戲捉撚咗個女主角入叢林屌閪最敬業！！！！！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有故事？磨牙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係，之前有人爆過，女主角而家仲好紅（喺蝗國 ）</blockquote><br />\n點解咁耐仲未有人郁佢?<br />\n之前唔係連宋祖英都搞? 都仲可以生勾勾企係到<br />\n條友係咪咁撚大勢力"},{"pid":"a66c930051cb013439c920e753c8c6b4e4ff0f5f","tid":56801,"uid":7081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有故事？磨牙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係，之前有人爆過，女主角而家仲好紅（喺蝗國 ）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未聽過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾時開名"},{"pid":"9b56933214851d4cdd5e03c8025c5b2f972b7a59","tid":56801,"uid":40273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有故事？磨牙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係，之前有人爆過，女主角而家仲好紅（喺蝗國 ）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未聽過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係喺網台聽返嚟，網台名係「red加先」，年幾有個節目，如果我冇記錯係「203040」講過，而爆料者係個電影幕後工作人員，好似叫肥Kel&hellip;(帶頭盔，因為時間太耐，唔sure係咪呢個節目"},{"pid":"ba485bdca3a4c3988923a74f2350e33f2fa7041c","tid":56801,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:50:50.000Z","msg":"拍幾個shot就頂唔順話辛苦<br />\n咁真係過份左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬成crew人陪緊你㗎<br />\n<br />\n成龍當年拍戲嚟講真係落力<br />\n係去左荷里活，荷里活唔俾佢咁逐個shot咁翻拍先開始差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家老左你仲想點<br />\n<br />\n但份人就真係中國奴才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c9cde4030b342af02463866fa2e4f6bdecb297","tid":56801,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係，之前有人爆過，女主角而家仲好紅（喺蝗國 ）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未聽過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係喺網台聽返嚟，網台名係「red加先」，年幾有個節目，如果我冇記錯係「203040」講過，而爆料者係個電影幕後工作人員，好似叫肥Kel&hellip;(帶頭盔，因為時間太耐，唔sure係咪呢個節目</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你咁仔細講邊度聽返來又唔講係邊個女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發下夢都好啊"},{"pid":"dd001dddedf0645a1a6567f03e05e962eef97522","tid":56801,"uid":40273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係，之前有人爆過，女主角而家仲好紅（喺蝗國 ）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未聽過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係喺網台聽返嚟，網台名係「red加先」，年幾有個節目，如果我冇記錯係「203040」講過，而爆料者係個電影幕後工作人員，好似叫肥Kel&hellip;(帶頭盔，因為時間太耐，唔sure係咪呢個節目</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗰集個topic好似係叫'蟲哥xxx'"},{"pid":"d4c03f85877f0c6075782980c54d53e452a0ffca","tid":56801,"uid":40273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:59:25.000Z","msg":"以前細個好鍾意睇佢d戲，到回歸後條撚樣淨係識奶共，見到佢都眼火爆"},{"pid":"c4ed0784d223112ae9888dff3e0cc90cd93fff1f","tid":56801,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:49:22.000Z","msg":"屌~ 佢自己個成家班唔撚係係片場作威作福咩<br />\n<br />\n分黨分派, 自成一個[黑]勢力[/黑]<br />\n<br />\n之前90s 娛樂圈既人出黎反黑, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">一定唔係指無份囉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n家下就拖住個督仔, 幫個督仔抓撈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"h